sections.content:
Most people are remarkably unproductive.
‎
You guys think you’re “busy”
‎
You’re not.
‎
As someone who’s genuinely busy I can tell you I achieve 10x the average person does per day. Hence me having 50x the income.
‎
You will learn how to do the same in here.
‎
You think you “have no time”.
‎
But you just haven’t learned how to use your time yet.
‎
